Package org.krysalis.barcode4j.saxon8

This package contains an extension for the SAXON 8.x XSLT Processor from Michael Kay for creating barcodes in SVG format during XSL transformations.

Package org.krysalis.barcode4j.saxon8 Description

This package contains an extension for the SAXON 8.x XSLT Processor from Michael Kay for creating barcodes in SVG format during XSL transformations.

See the SAXON use case for information on how to use the extension.
